extends layout

block content
	div#content.container
		div.row
			div.col-sm-2
				button(id="btn_location" class="btn btn-warning" type="button")
					i(class="glyphicon glyphicon-screenshot") &nbsp;
					span Find hospitals near me
			div.col-sm-10
				div.input-group
					input(type="text" name="address" id="address" placeholder="Address" class="form-control")
					span.input-group-btn
						button(id="btn_search" class="btn btn-primary" type="button") Go
		div.row
			div.col-sm-12
				div#finding_location.alert.alert-warning Finding location
		div.row
			div.col-sm-12
				div#hospitals
					div.alert.alert-info The Code4SA City Press Hospital Finder App uses data from the Department of Health's 2011/2012 survey of its hospitals and clinics to help you find the best medical services close by. Simply enter an address above and click "Go", else click "Find hospitals near me" for us to detect your current location.
	
	script(id="hospital-template" type="text/x-handlebars-template")
		include hospital.html